Package com.linkly.pos.sdk.models.transaction

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CashRequest
    Cash-out only transaction.
    DepositRequest
    Deposit cash and/or cheques.
    FollowUpTransactionRequest
    Transaction request which is linked to an original transaction via a reference number.
    PreAuthCancelRequest
    Cancel a PreAuthRequest.
    PreAuthCompletionRequest
    Complete a PreAuthRequest for an amount of PreAuthManipulationRequest.amount
    PreAuthExtendRequest
    Renew the expiry date of a PreAuthRequest.
    PreAuthInquiryRequest
    Perform an inquiry or verify the amount of a PreAuthRequest.
    PreAuthManipulationRequest
    Abstract base class for pre-authorisation requests which perform some action on an existing pre-authorisation.
    PreAuthPartialCancelRequest
    Reduce a PreAuthRequest for an amount of PreAuthManipulationRequest.amount
    PreAuthRequest
    Create a new pre-authorisation.
    PreAuthSummaryRequest
    Perform an inquiry on all existing pre-authorisations for informational purposes.
    PreAuthTopUpRequest
    Increase a PreAuthRequest for an amount of PreAuthManipulationRequest.getAmount() cents.
    PurchaseRequest
    Purchase transaction.
    RefundRequest
    Refund transaction.
    RetrieveTransactionRequest
    Retrieve a historical transaction result.
    TippingOptions
    Provides up to three tipping options to present to the customer as a percentage of the total purchase amount.
    TransactionFlags
    The flags that apply to the transaction.
    TransactionRequest
    Base request used for all transactions.
    TransactionResponse  
    VoidRequest
    Void transaction prior to settlement.
